OL,9,FA man who raped and sexually exploited
OL,10,Fteenage girls in Wolverhampton has
OL,11,Fbeen jailed for 18 years.
OL,13,FGurpreet Randhawa, who is 21 and from
OL,14,FWellington Road in the city, raped two
OL,15,F15-year-old girls and threatened a 12-
OL,16,Fyear-old girl into sending him
OL,17,Fexplicit photos of herself.
OL,19,FHe raped one of the 15-year-old girls
OL,20,Fon three separate occasions between
OL,21,FAugust and September last year.
