OL,6,FWest Midlands Police praised the
OL,7,Fbravery of the 12-year-old girl, who
OL,8,Ftold her school what Randhawa, who
OL,9,Fwent by the name "Ziggy", had been
OL,10,Fdoing.
OL,12,FThe school alerted the force, and
OL,13,Fpolice say they quickly identified
OL,14,FRandhawa, who was arrested the same
OL,15,Fday.
OL,17,FOfficers say Randhawa, who contacted
OL,18,Fthe 12-year-old girl through social
OL,19,Fmedia, used other names on the
OL,20,Fplatform, where he engaged in
OL,21,Fconversations of a sexual nature.
