OL,6,FHe sent inappropriate videos and
OL,7,Fpictures of himself and threatened to
OL,8,Fharm the 12-year-old girl if she
OL,9,Fdidn't comply, and he also encouraged
OL,10,Fher to ask friends to do the same.
OL,12,FRandhawa pleaded guilty to four
OL,13,Foffences of rape, two of taking
OL,14,Findecent images of a child, a further
OL,15,Ftwo offences of sharing indecent
OL,16,Fimages and engaging in sexual
OL,17,Fcommunication.
OL,19,FThe offences took place between July
OL,20,F2024 and September 2025.
